text: Alberina Syla (born 4 September 1997) is a German-born Kosovan footballer who plays as a forward for Regionalliga Süd club Eintracht Frankfurt and the Kosovo women's national team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:German women's footballers Category:German people of Kosovan descent
